\f0\fs24 \

\f3\fs20 Sanders
\f0\fs24 \

\f3\fs20 Mr. Sanders has called for a moratorium on deportations pending a review of the current immigration system. He also supports the reinstatement and expansion of the DACA program, which protected from deportation people who were brought into the United States as children.
\f0\fs24 \

\f3\fs20 In addition, he has backed the movement to abolish federal agencies like Immigration and Customs Enforcement and Customs and Border Protection.
\f0\fs24 \

\f3\fs20 Mass incarceration
\f0\fs24 \

\f3\fs20 Biden
\f0\fs24 \

