\f0\fs24 \

\f3\fs20 In contrast to Mr. Sanders, however, he does not want to legalize marijuana.
\f0\fs24 \

\f3\fs20 Sanders
\f0\fs24 \

\f3\fs20 Mr. Sanders has promised to cut the national prison population in half and end mass incarceration. To do that, he wants to abolish the death penalty, three-strikes laws and mandatory minimum sentences, among other measures.
\f0\fs24 \

\f3\fs20 Gun control
\f0\fs24 \

\f3\fs20 Biden
\f0\fs24 \

