\f0\fs24 \

\f3\fs20   ''There are maybe 10 to 20 H.B.C.U.s facing being shuttered that don't have those fields,'' said Jerry Crawford II, a professor of journalism and a director of the multicultural scholars program at the University of Kansas. 
