\f3\fs20   Well, you are quite right. We have a new vision for America and at a time when we have three people in this country owning more wealth than the bottom half of America, while 500,000 people are sleeping out on the streets today we think it is time for change, real change.
\f0\fs24 \

\f3\fs20   And by that I mean that healthcare in my view is a human right and we have got to pass a Medicare for all single-payer system.
\f0\fs24 \

\f3\fs20   (APPLAUSE)
\f0\fs24 \

