\f3\fs20   SANDERS:
\f0\fs24 \

\f3\fs20   People who have healthcare under Medicare for all will have no premiums, no deductibles, no copayments, no out of expe--out-of-pocket expenses. Yes, they will pay more in taxes but less in healthcare for what they get.
