Some closer to Mr. O\'92Rourke\'92s age were less convinced. Standing near the back, Erin Cruz, 41, sized up Mr. O\'92Rourke \'97 and then praised the septuagenarian socialist senator, Bernie Sanders.\
\'93I\'92m looking for someone to be as progressive as Bernie,\'94 Ms. Cruz said, tugging on a Red Hot Chili Peppers shirt.\
Actually, she amended, perhaps just Bernie himself.\
